ed nephropathy.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/192851/', '', 'Tamsulosin, Tinidazole, Ascorbic acid, Metronidazole, Simeprevir, Sulfadiazine, Lactic acid, Mitapivat, Clindamycin, Ciclopirox, Vemurafenib, More', 'Iodamide, Tyropanoic acid, Ethiodized oil, Iopanoic acid, Iopodic acid, Metrizamide', 1767369485);
